Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Gerald Ford, the new man in the White House, 1974
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yqn5j
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 23 Aug 1974
Campaign biographies, and some new revelations about President Gerald Ford's past come to light, including the fact he was christened Leslie King Junior.